rows.label: qst200717_msg0001
rows.name:
The mushroom dish we all
ate was so delicious-ppo!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0002
rows.name: Idaten ate as heartily as ever!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0004
rows.name:
It musta been, since you
ate three people's worth!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0005
rows.name:
You ate that much, so you
must be satisfied, right?

rows.label: qst200717_msg0006
rows.name: Idaten ate as heartily as ever.

rows.label: qst200717_msg0007
rows.name: Is your stomach and heart full?

rows.label: qst200717_msg0008
rows.name:
Idaten ate with a good
appetite as always!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0010
rows.name: No, Idaten is not satisfied yet-ppo!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0011
rows.name:
There are many foods in this world
that Idaten doesn't know about-ppo!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0012
rows.name: I want to find more new foods-ppo!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0014
rows.name:
Also... Idaten seems to be popular
with the Nopon, so I want to keep my
title as the speed-eating hero-ppo!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0015
rows.name:
I will always accept
challenges from Tora,
Maumau... and you, my Driver-ppo!

rows.label: qst200717_msg0016
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Popopop... Speed-eating contests are
a great deal because you can eat
lots of mushrooms for free-ppo!
